properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 5 at 6:36PM EST until January 6 at 10:00PM EST by NWS Buffalo NY
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds to 35 knots and waves 11 to 15 feet expected.

* WHERE...The open waters of Lake Ontario from Hamlin Beach to
the Saint Lawrence River, and the nearshore waters of Lake
Ontario from Mexico Bay to the Saint Lawrence River.

* WHEN...From 7 AM to 10 PM EST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 7 AM TO 10 PM EST MONDAY
